{"id": 1761, "genre": 1000, "title": "即使知道没啥依据，但你忍不住还是会有哪些乡愁怀旧式感慨？", "description": "当文青想回到海明威、毕加索时代，海明威们却想回到拜伦、雨果时代，而拜伦们总想着回到文艺复兴，黄金时代总是在过去。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 8120, "comment_count": 35, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201706271024177lXeB6zitEcoIWdj.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-27T17:00:48Z", "questions": [{"id": 2503, "title": "即使知道没啥依据，但你忍不住还是会有哪些乡愁怀旧式感慨？", "content": "你觉得哪些乡愁怀旧式感慨，其实都没什么依据？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 216241, "content": "小时候看的那一版电视剧，总是最经典的版本", "image": "img/option/option/20170627105726vpXEAM2Jkj1Voglc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216242, "content": "前时代总是科学天才云集，当代似乎找不出多少聪明的脑瓜来", "image": "img/option/option/20170627104630rtTLZbUwPOyE5DSg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216252, "content": "小时候零食比现在的更好吃", "image": "img/option/option/20170627104721ECpjm5IPQLZ1rFs2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216253, "content": "过去的人/乡下的人总是更淳朴善良", "image": "img/option/option/20170627104804nFGaw1KYhNdUby9j.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216254, "content": "小时候看的动画总是比现在的动画要好看得多", "image": "img/option/option/20170627104843jUgN5RHBWOZT7wXv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216255, "content": "在异地吃的家乡美食总觉得不够正宗，即使做法没区别", "image": "img/option/option/20170627104934e1mJcIOoBfj0vXUP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216256, "content": "上世纪的音乐比良莠不齐的现代音乐水平要高得多", "image": "img/option/option/201706271054593SQdJe7VYRZKbXzE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216257, "content": "现在制作精良的网游反而没有小时候的红白机好玩", "image": "img/option/option/201706271057126Dxjhi0aqdJQX5ws.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}